Description: See why so many travelers make Khach san Kim Bang their guest house of choice when visiting Thu Dau Mot. Providing an ideal mix of value, comfort and convenience, it offers an array of amenities designed for travelers like you. The rooms offer air conditioning, and getting online is possible, as free wifi is available, allowing you to rest and refresh with ease. Khach san Kim Bang features a 24 hour front desk and baggage storage. Guests arriving by vehicle have access to free parking. When you’re feeling hungry, be sure to check out Tiamo Restaurant, BONBA Tea Bar, and Grand Square Convention Center & Restaurants, which are some diners that are popular with locals and out-of-towners alike. Should time allow, Hoi Khanh Pagoda is a popular attraction that is within walking distance. We’re sure you’ll enjoy your stay at Khach san Kim Bang as you experience all of the things Thu Dau Mot has to offer.
